commit.message: Prepare version v0.20.0
Update to latest cibuildwheel to try to fix builds for Python 3.12
Prepare version v0.20.0rc1
Fix #245, never introduce new nodes during discard
Fix #268 2, do not rely on well implemented __ne__ for keys in pmaps, instead do explicit inversion of equality comparison when checking for inequality
Fix #268, decrease the pmap size by the number of items removed rather than one to avoid inconsistencies in case of bad equality implementations in contained instances
Officially drop python 3.7 support
